00:24:14,041 --> 00:24:16,916
- Vash: REPEATED TRAGEDIES,
REPEATED PAIN.

350
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:19,250
THE WISHES OF A MAN
ARE SO STRONG

351
00:24:19,333 --> 00:24:21,583
AND YET SO FRAIL AND WEAK.

352
00:24:21,666 --> 00:24:22,916
TO LIVE,

353
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,916
TO STAY ALIVE.

354
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:28,791
WHO WOULD HAVE KNOWN THAT
SURVIVAL WAS THIS HARD?

355
00:24:28,875 --> 00:24:30,541
THIS PAINFUL?

356
00:24:30,625 --> 00:24:32,250
I MUST CHOOSE.

357
00:24:32,333 --> 00:24:34,250
I MUST MAKE THE CHOICE.

358
00:24:34,333 --> 00:24:37,583
IN THE MOMENT THAT
INTERTWINES LIFE AND DEATH,

359
00:24:37,666 --> 00:24:40,125
CAN I CHOOSE TO
REMAIN A HUMAN?

